{% # Separator block v1.2.0 %}

{% comment %}
  Changelog
  - v1.2.0 — top-margin override range narrowed to `0…100` (step 2): the override is an absolute value that replaces the section rhythm; negatives (overlap) dropped — no block-level use case. Tighten with a small positive below the rhythm; use a `spacer` for larger gaps. Pairs with `utility--block-layout-vars` v1.2.1 (emit on `> 0`).
  - v1.1.0 — top-margin override range changed to `-100…100` (was `0…200`): negative values pull a block tighter than the section rhythm; the 100–200 push range is dropped (use a `spacer` block for larger gaps). Step stays 2 — Shopify caps ranges at 101 steps. Pairs with `utility--block-layout-vars` v1.2.0 (emit on `!= 0`). See `.context/docs/schema-conventions.md` § Top-spacing pair.
  - v1.0.0 — initial
{% endcomment %}

